  "texts": [
    "We omitted the Trial set in our experiments, since it was included in the Train set.",
    "For training and tuning the final models, we used the Train and Dev sets.",
    "The two Eval sets were used by the GermEval 2023 organizers to compute the final scores for Subtask 1 (Eval set 1) and Subtask 2 (Eval set 2).",
    "While the two Eval sets contained the same samples, the organizers provided gold cues with Eval set 2.",
    "We used the Llama 2 model family (Touvron, Martin, et al., 2023), a set of large language models pretrained on a corpus of two trillion tokens with a context length of 4096 tokens."
